# Graphify Discipline

This project uses a graphify knowledge graph in `graphify-out/`.

- Before architecture/codebase decisions, review `graphify-out/GRAPH_REPORT.md`.
- If `graphify-out/wiki/index.md` exists, prefer navigating wiki pages first.
- After structural or code changes, run `make graphify-update`.
- Keep graph artifacts updated in the same task when structure changes.
